Mod] Students [0.1] [Students]

by Peppy » Thu Aug 31, 2017 05:51
Students

Description

Students is a minetest mod to perform various actions on a group of players.

Group actions

    Group grant/revoke creative privilege.
    Freeze/unfreeze your students.
    Gather together your students.
    Heal your students.
    More to come...
    
Kooperation ist angefragt von Birgit Lachner :-)


